### 2. forecastRainEcmwf_each

**用途**: 获取各子流域的格网预报降雨过程
**请求方式**: GET
**请求路径**: `http://10.20.2.153:8089/modelPlatf/forecast/forecastRainEcmwf/each`
**输入参数**:

- st: 开始时间 (Date, 必填)
- ed: 结束时间 (Date, 必填)
- businessCode: 业务模型编码 (String, 可选)
**输出结果**:

```json
{
    "success": true,
    "code": "200",
    "message": "请求成功",
    "data": {
        "WH001": [
            {"time": "2023-12-01 00:00:00", "value": 5.2},
            {"time": "2023-12-01 01:00:00", "value": 8.5}
        ],
        "WH002": [
            {"time": "2023-12-01 00:00:00", "value": 3.1},
            {"time": "2023-12-01 01:00:00", "value": 6.8}
        ]
    }
}
```

### 6. contourRain_today

**用途**: 获取8点以后降雨等值面
**请求方式**: GET
**请求路径**: `http://10.20.2.153:8089/modelPlatf/contour/rainProc/today`
**输入参数**:

- t: 时间 (Date, 可选, 默认当前时间, 格式: yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss)
**输出结果**:

```json
{
    "success": true,
    "code": "200",
    "message": "请求成功",
    "data": {
        "type": "FeatureCollection",
        "features": [
            {
                "type": "Feature",
                "properties": {"value": 10, "color": "#00FF00"},
                "geometry": {"type": "Polygon", "coordinates": [[[114.5, 35.2]]]}
            }
        ]
    }
}
```

### 22. modelRainArea_getByPlan

**用途**: 获取指定方案的各子流域降雨过程(无需登录)
**请求方式**: GET
**请求路径**: `http://10.20.2.153:8089/modelPlatf/model/modelRainArea/getByPlan`
**输入参数**:

- planCode: 方案编码 (String, 必填)
**输出结果**:

```json
{
    "success": true,
    "code": "200",
    "message": "请求成功",
    "data": {
        "WH001": [
            {"time": "2023-12-01 00:00:00", "value": 5.2},
            {"time": "2023-12-01 01:00:00", "value": 8.5}
        ],
        "WH002": [
            {"time": "2023-12-01 00:00:00", "value": 3.1},
            {"time": "2023-12-01 01:00:00", "value": 6.8}
        ]
    }
}
```
